item.description: Netcommunity OG410X and OG810X series (Netcommunity OG410Xa, OG410Xi, OG810Xa, and OG810Xi firmware Ver.2.28 and earlier) allow an attacker on the adjacent network to execute an arbitrary OS command via a specially crafted config file.
